{"TopicId":215331,"ForumId":197,"TopicTitle":"Orbits can be changed in Tracking Station","CreatedByName":"Tazooka","CreatedById":226666,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-17T16:03:00Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Tazooka","CreatedById":226666,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-17T16:03:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nv0.1.1.0 bug\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can still adjust and control ships in the tracking station by pressing Z and X to set the throttle\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSee video:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022113\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/ryfQpxjj72o?feature=oembed\u0022 title=\u0022Kerbal Space Program 2 v0.1.1.0 - Changing orbits in Tracking Station\u0022 width=\u0022200\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"LameLefty","CreatedById":57336,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-17T20:10:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAdd SHIFT to the list of controls that affect the throttle. I tried to rename a vessel and added throttle with each capital letter.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-03-18T20:55:40Z\u0022 title=\u002203/18/2023 08:55  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00221 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 18, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by LameLefty\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003Etypos\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tazooka","CreatedById":226666,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-17T20:57:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224261256\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022215331\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221679083857\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002257336\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022LameLefty\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n44 minutes ago, LameLefty said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAdd SHIFT to the list of controls that affect the throttle. I tried to rename a vessels and addled throttle with each capital letter.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGood spot, I didn\u0027t realise this happened too! This really needs to be fixed as I\u0027ve already messed up one of my orbits by accident\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"JoeSchmuckatelli","CreatedById":154477,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-22T15:27:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYep - that\u0027s a problem\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso - changing names does not actually change the names of vessels.\u00A0 They revert.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"didkodidko","CreatedById":226055,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-04-07T13:24:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat are the QA doing?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}